result.description: **Another quality release from your friends at the Classic Hentai Archival Project!** CHAP rises from the dead! Here is our first release in over a year: episode 4 of the Little Mermaid Series titled "Shining May". Idol becomes famous, yadda yadda yadda. Brand new stereo audio mix sourced from the 1988 Laserdisc reissue of this and other LMS episodes including "Barefoot After School" and IQ315, along with a new Domesday capture, film grain and all! More to come, stay tuned! We hope you enjoy our first release in some time. On to the next CHAP/CLAP release. **Video sources**: 1988 LaserDisc release (Domesday Duplicator capture) **Audio sources**: 1988 LaserDisc release (Domesday Duplicator PCM capture) **Subtitles**: English translation by Incense Idol Subs (courtesy of Vaye; QCd by elgringo)
